title: Animals Aboard with Dr. Harry
overview: Animals Aboard with Dr. Harry goes behind the scenes of the multi-million-dollar animal travel industry to unearth a goldmine of touching stories of pets and animals who need to travel for work, play, medical reasons, or family reunions. The trailer shows pets who've been reunited with their loved ones, as well as exotic zoo animals that have been transported, and the return of rehabilitated marine life.
